{"comments":"HoverAudio — Audio triggered on hover.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nDescribes sounds to play when hovering over an element:\n- Enter sound (mouse enters)\n- Leave sound (mouse exits)\n- Loop while hovering\n\n## Audio Sources\n\nAudio can come from URL or inline base64 data.\nVolume is normalized 0.0 to 1.0.\n\n## Fade Behavior\n\nFades smooth out abrupt audio starts/stops:\n- fadeInMs: gradual volume increase on enter\n- fadeOutMs: gradual volume decrease on leave\n\n## Examples\n\n```purescript\n-- Dog card plays bark on hover\ndogBark = hoverAudioEnter (HoverAudioUrl \"/sounds/bark.mp3\") 0.5\n\n-- Ambient loop while hovering\nambientHover = hoverAudioLoop (HoverAudioUrl \"/sounds/ambient.ogg\") 0.3\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["enterSound",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Audio"],"HoverAudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["leaveSound",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Audio"],"HoverAudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["loopSound",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","HoverEffect","Audio"],"HoverAudioSource"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["volume",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["fadeInMs",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["fadeOutMs",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Re